metadata.name: The Cycle of Nihil (colour)
metadata.description:
Stare at this long enough, then look away and things will start to move... 

Nihil has arrived at a place we all come to eventually. He is dead.

Past memories and sense of self fade into nothing as he sinks through the timeless void.

His body separates and dissolves into new lifeforms that spread out and fill the space, they are as much apart of him as he is of them.

Out of all the new beings who now inhabit his awareness, he focuses most on the one who sits calmly in the center beneath a knowing tree, he names him 'Nihil'.
